oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Kinzel Joseph A. Kinzel grave, 1902.
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Grave of engineer Joseph A. Kinzel who was fatally injured when A K &N Railway engine #25 overturned on February 27, 1902. He died on March 11, 1902, and was buried at Millertown, Knox County, TN. March 12, 1902.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Graves; Funeral rites & ceremonies; Flower arrangements; Tombs & sepulchral monuments;
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Knox County Two Centuries Photograph Project
